AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Voltage Phase Unbalance Violation Limit
AFAttributeTemplate.Description: Voltage phase unbalance limit before triggering PI Event Frame to track violation event..

AFAnalysisTemplate.Name: Current Calculations
AFAnalysisTemplate.Description: Analysis that performs current related calculations.

AFAnalysisRule.VariableMapping: CurrentPhaseA||% Load Current Phase A;CurrentPhaseB||% Load Current Phase B;CurrentPhaseC||% Load Current Phase C;TotalCurrent||Total Current;

AFAnalysisTemplate.Name: OSIDemo_SimulatedData
AFAnalysisTemplate.Description: Analysis that generates simulated data for voltages and currents.

AFAnalysisRule.VariableMapping: VoltagePhaseA||Voltage Phase A;VoltagePhaseB||Voltage Phase B;VoltagePhaseC||Voltage Phase C;CurrentPhaseA||Current Phase A;CurrentPhaseB||Current Phase B;CurrentPhaseC||Current Phase C;

AFAnalysisTemplate.Name: OSIdemo_SimulatedData_Power
AFAnalysisTemplate.Description: Analysis that generates simulated data for power.

AFAnalysisRule.ConfigString: Power := Avg('Voltage Phase A','Voltage Phase B','Voltage Phase C') * Avg('Current Phase A','Current Phase B','Current Phase C') * 0.8; ReactivePower := Power * 0.25/0.8;

AFAnalysisTemplate.Name: Voltage Phase Limit Violation High
AFAnalysisTemplate.Description: PI Event Frame tracks when voltage is higher than predefined violation limit.

AFAnalysisRule.ConfigString: StartTrigger := 'Voltage Phase A' > 'Voltage Limit Violation High' OR 'Voltage Phase B' > 'Voltage Limit Violation High' OR 'Voltage Phase C' > 'Voltage Limit Violation High';

AFAnalysisTemplate.Name: Voltage Phase Limit Violation Low
AFAnalysisTemplate.Description: PI Event Frame tracks when voltage is lower than predefined violation limit.

AFAnalysisRule.ConfigString: StartTrigger := 'Voltage Phase A' < 'Voltage Limit Violation Low' OR 'Voltage Phase B' < 'Voltage Limit Violation Low' OR 'Voltage Phase C' < 'Voltage Limit Violation Low';

AFAnalysisTemplate.Name: Voltage Phase Unbalance
AFAnalysisTemplate.Description: Analysis that performs voltage phase unbalance calculation.

AFAnalysisTemplate.Name: Voltage Phase Unbalance Event
AFAnalysisTemplate.Description: PI Event Frame tracks when voltage phase unbalance is greater than predefined violation limit.

AFAnalysisRule.ConfigString: StartTrigger := 'Voltage Phase Unbalance' > 'Voltage Phase Unbalance Violation Limit';

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Current
AFAttributeTemplate.Description: Current the transformer is running on.

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Latitude
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT [%Attribute%] FROM [Substation Transformer Information] WHERE [Substation Transformer] = '%Element%'

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Rated Current
AFAttributeTemplate.Description: Highest current transformer was desgiend to run at.

AFAnalysisRule.VariableMapping: Current||Current;VoltagePhaseAOut||Voltage Phase A Out;VoltagePhaseBOut||Voltage Phase B Out;VoltagePhaseCOut||Voltage Phase C Out;
